24:57.208 --> 25:00.375
[exclaims, grunting]

25:03.333 --> 25:04.750
-[snaps]
-[bone crunches]

25:04.833 --> 25:06.458
-[groaning]
-[all exclaiming]

25:09.125 --> 25:11.916
Mana... Mana...

25:12.000 --> 25:14.666
